data.description: Welcome to Marquis Hills! This home has all the features you need. The 1st floor has open design; a large coat closet & powder room are conveniently placed off the entry hall, and the great room is an open space you see from the large kitchen with eat-in island and dining room.  Upstairs, four bedrooms that provide all the room you need. Owner’s suite has in-suite bath that features a double bowl vanity, oversized shower & two huge walk-in closets! An ample hall bath, linen closet & laundry complete the upper level. Marquis Hills is right behind Target/Marquis Shopping Center in Williamsburg offering convenience to entertainment and Shopping.  Just 15 min to Ft Eustis and 1 mile to I-64.
